    <!-- About Activity -->
    <string name="about"><![CDATA[<p><b>Hentoid</b> is a Hentai Manga reader & archiving app.<br />Hentoid was originally created by <b>Cesar Arasaki</b>.</p><p>Hentoid offers you a way to archive H-Manga to your device without the worry of it ever being removed from your collection.<br />Hentoid was previously known as FAKKUDroid, before support was added for Pururin and Hitomi.</p><br /><p>While initially designed to work with <b>FAKKU</b>, <b>Pururin</b> and <b>Hitomi</b>, support for <b>nhentai</b> and <b>tsumino</b> has also been added after FAKKU going legit and Pururin getting abandoned.</p><p><b>Notes:</b><br />In regards to tsumino - you will need to solve the captcha for now, but we are experimenting with other methods as well.<br />FAKKU has dropped support for free content, and while support for FAKKU Books or Subscriptions is not currently planned, this may change in the future.]]></string>
